<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 1003/81 of 10 April 1981 defining the operative event in the case of the sale of cereals and rice held in store by intervention agencies </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1003/81, milles m&auml;&auml;ratletakse sekkumisametite ladustatava teravilja ja riisi m&uuml;&uuml;gi rakendusjuht 10. aprill 1981 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2727/75 of 29 October 1975 on the common organization of the market in cereals (1), as last amended by the Act of Accession of Greece, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 29. oktoobri 1975. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2727/75 teraviljaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud Kreeka &uuml;hinemisaktiga, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1418/76 of 21 June 1976 on the common organization of the market in rice (2) as last amended by the Act of Accession of Greece, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 21. juuni 1976. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1418/76 riisituru &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (2) viimati muudetud Kreeka &uuml;hinemisaktiga, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 878/77 of 26 April 1977 on the exchange rates to be applied in agriculture (3), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 850/81 (4), and in particular Article 4 (3) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 26. aprilli 1977. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 878/77 p&otilde;llumajanduses kohaldatavate vahetuskursside kohta, (3) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 850/81, (4) eriti selle artikli 4 l&otilde;iget 3, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 4 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 878/77 provides that, with regard to the effect on the rights and obligations existing at the time a representative rate is altered, the provisions of Council Regulation (EEC) No 1134/68 of 30 July 1968 laying down rules for the implementation of Regulation (EEC) No 653/68 on conditions for alterations to the value of the unit of account used for the common agricultural policy (5), adopted for altering the relationship between the parity of one Member State's currency and the value of the unit of account, shall apply; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 878/77 artikli 4 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatakse, et arvestades tasakaalustamiskursi m&otilde;ju muutmishetkel kehtivatele &otilde;igustele ja kohustustele, tuleb kohaldada &uuml;hises p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitikas kasutatava arvestus&uuml;hiku v&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmistingimusi k&auml;sitleva m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 653/68 rakenduseeskirju kehtestava n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuli 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 s&auml;tteid, mis on vastu v&otilde;etud liikmesriigi valuuta pariteedi ja arvestus&uuml;hiku v&auml;&auml;rtuse vahelise suhte muutmiseks; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 4 (2) of Regulation (EEC) No 1134/68 provides that the sums therein stated are to be paid by using the conversion rate in force at the time the transaction or part thereof was carried out; whereas, pursuant to Article 6 of the said Regulation, the time when a transaction is carried out is to be considered as being the date on which occurs the event, as defined by Community rules or, in the absence of and pending adoption of such rules, by the rules of the Member State concerned, in which the amount involved in the transaction becomes due and payable; whereas, however, Article 4 (3) of Regulation (EEC) No 878/77 permits derogation from the above provisions; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 artikli 4 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatakse, et k&otilde;nealustes s&auml;tetes nimetatud summade maksmisel tuleb kasutada tehingu v&otilde;i tehingu osa sooritamise ajal j&otilde;us olnud &uuml;mberarvestuskurssi; nimetatud m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 6 kohaselt k&auml;sitatakse tehingu sooritamise ajana kuup&auml;eva, mil ilmneb asjaolu, mis on m&auml;&auml;ratletud &uuml;henduse eeskirjades v&otilde;i nende eeskirjade puudumisel v&otilde;i kuni nende vastuv&otilde;tmiseni asjaomase liikmesriigi &otilde;igusaktides esitatud m&auml;&auml;ratlusele tekib kohustus tasuda tehinguga seotud summa; m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 878/77 artikli 4 l&otilde;ikes 3 lubatakse eespool nimetatud s&auml;tetest siiski erandeid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in the case of products held by the intervention agencies and resold by way of invitation to tender on the Community market or for export, any alteration to the representative rates after award but before the products are taken over by the successful tenderer automatically results in an alteration to the tender price and to the refunds fixed in advance, as the case may be; whereas adjustments of this may constitute considerable changes in the economic data used by operators in their calculations; whereas, in order to avoid such consequences, it is appropriate, in the context of such invitations to tender, to derogate from the rule laid down in Article 6 of Regulation (EEC) No 1134/68 and to select the closing date for submission of tenders under each partial invitation to tender as the operative event; </inglise>
<eesti> toodete puhul, mis on sekkumisametite valduses ja mis m&uuml;&uuml;akse pakkumismenetluse teel edasi &uuml;henduse turule v&otilde;i ekspordiks, toob tasakaalustamiskursside muutus, mis toimub pakkumiste vastuv&otilde;tmise j&auml;rel, kuid enne toodete &uuml;lev&otilde;tmist eduka pakkuja poolt, automaatselt kaasa pakkumishinna ja vajaduse korral eelnevalt kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud toetuste muutuse; k&otilde;nealused kohandused v&otilde;ivad p&otilde;hjustada arvestatavaid muutusi majandusandmetes, mida ettev&otilde;tjad oma arvutustes kasutavad; selliste tagaj&auml;rgede v&auml;ltimiseks on k&otilde;nealuste pakkumismenetluste kontekstis asjakohane kehtestada erand m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 artiklis 6 s&auml;testatud eeskirjast ja valida iga osalise pakkumismenetluse puhul rakendusjuhuks pakkumiste esitamise t&auml;htp&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to reflect the requirements of the present economic situation, provision should be made for the said provisions to have retroactive effect in respect to tenders submitted and refunds fixed in advance under invitations to tender current since 17 December 1980, where the quantities awarded have not yet been taken over by the successful tenderer; </inglise>
<eesti> praeguse majandusliku olukorra arvessev&otilde;tmiseks tuleks s&auml;testada, et k&otilde;nealuseid s&auml;tteid kohaldatakse tagasiulatuvalt alates 17. detsembrist 1980 toimunud pakkumismenetluste raames esitatud pakkumiste ja eelnevalt kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud toetuste suhtes, kui edukas pakkuja ei ole m&auml;&auml;ratud kogust veel &uuml;le v&otilde;tnud; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Cereals, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las teraviljaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The representative rate to be applied under invitations to tender opened pursuant to Article 3 (1) of Council Regulation (EEC) No 2738/75 (6) and of Council Regulation (EEC) No 1424/76 (7), for the purposes of accepting tenders submitted and of determining the export refunds where advance fixing was applied for at the time the tender was submitted, shall be the representative rate in force on the final day for submitting tenders under the individual invitation to tender in question. </inglise>
<eesti> Tasakaalustamiskurss, mida kohaldatakse n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2738/75 (6) artikli 3 l&otilde;ike 1 ja n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1424/76 (7) kohaselt v&auml;ljakuulutatud pakkumismenetluste raames esitatud pakkumiste vastuv&otilde;tmiseks ja eksporditoetuste kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramiseks juhul, kui pakkumise esitamisel on taotletud toetuse eelnevat kinnitamist, on k&otilde;nealuse pakkumismenetluse pakkumiste esitamise t&auml;htp&auml;eval j&otilde;us olnud taskaalustamiskurss. </eesti>
<inglise> The provisions of this Article shall also apply to awards made since 17 December 1980, where the successful tenderer has not taken over the products by the date of entry into force of this Regulation. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva artikli s&auml;tteid kohaldatakse ka alates 17. detsembrist 1980 toimunud pakkumismenetluste suhtes, kui edukas pakkuja ei ole k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse j&otilde;ustumise kuup&auml;evaks tooteid &uuml;le v&otilde;tnud. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on 13 April 1981. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub 13. aprillil 1981. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 10 April 1981. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 10. aprill 1981 </eesti>
